ED_Title: Confirmation of the appointment of the Administrator of the United Nations Development Programme
ED_DecisionText: At its 95th plenary meeting, on 5 September 2025, the General Assembly decided to include the sub-item entitled “Confirmation of the appointment of the Administrator of the United Nations Development Programme” of the item entitled “Appointments to fill vacancies in subsidiary organs and other appointments” in the draft agenda of its eightieth session.
